     mappings from Son of ScheduleBuilder which have not been separated out
     into individual mappings files.
     
     When it comes time to write a preprocessor that uses these mappings (for
     example, one to add day-sort-orders to classes), it would probably be
     good to separate them out into their own files.
     
     The subject, division and course type mappings have already been
     separated out.
========================================================================== -->

